	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You won't need the CHR data.
<br />
<br />I dumped both PRG and CHR EPROMs from my M82 a few years ago. If you dump yours, please compare the data with mine to see whether there are any differences.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


